  <note line="23" original="na gaṇṭusakaraṇamattena (ka.)" reference-line="7" id="2">
    <extra></extra>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="vri" source="vipassana research institut">naṃ, evaṃ anatthataṃ. Kathañca pana, bhikkhave, anatthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ? Na ullikhitamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na dhovanamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na cīvaravicāraṇamattena</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="ka." source="cambodian">na gaṇṭusakaraṇamattena</alternative>
    </alternatives>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet> Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, evaṃ anatthataṃ. Kathañca pana, bhikkhave, anatthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ? Na ullikhitamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na dhovanamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na cīvaravicāraṇamattena </snippet>
